Airiti Library華藝線上圖書館





































													篇名
												


傳統啟蒙教材對國小學童識字能力與國語文學業成就效應之研究






														並列篇名
													


															A Study on Traditional Enlightened Teaching Material for Promoting the Literacy Ability and Chinese Learning Effect of Elementary School Students.
														




														作者
													


															陳秀絨

														




													關鍵字
												



														傳統啟蒙教材 ； 故事繪本 ； 中文識字能力 ； 國語文學業成就 ； traditional enlightened teaching material ； picturebook ； Chinese literacy ； Chinese learning effect
													




													出版品名稱
												


														國立臺北教育大學教育政策與管理研究所學位論文
													




													捲期/出版年月
												


碩士													




														學位類別
													

碩士




														指導教授
													

林於弘 博士




													內容語文
												

繁體中文




														中文摘要
													

摘要
本研究主要的目的，在於探討傳統啟蒙教材能否促進國小學童國語文能力之提昇，其次，則在探討傳統啟蒙教材對提昇國小學童識字能力與國語文學習的成效，並根據研究結果提出相關建議。
本研究以一所國小一、三年級各二個班級的學生為對象，採用準實驗研究法（quasi-experimental method），將受試者分為實驗組以及控制組二組，分別施以傳統啟蒙教材與故事繪本閱讀指導。實驗過程採用「中文年級認字量表」與國語文定期考試成績為評量工具，並以獨立樣本單因子共變數分析比較不同組別學生在「中文年級認字量表」之得分以及國語文成績之差異，分析傳統啟蒙教材對國小一、三年級學童之識字能力與國語文學習之成效；並從訪談參與實驗老師、研究對象填寫之「學習回饋單」中，以瞭解其對傳統啟蒙教材學習的心得與建議。
研究結果顯示：
一、一年級學習傳統啟蒙教材之實驗組學生，其中文識字能力優於故事繪本閱讀之控制組學生。
二、三年級學習傳統啟蒙教材之實驗組學生，其中文識字能力優於故事繪本閱讀之控制組學生。
三、一年級學習傳統啟蒙教材之實驗組學生，其國語文學習成效優於故事繪本閱讀之控制組學生。
四、三年級學習傳統啟蒙教材之實驗組學生，其國語文學習成效優於故事繪本閱讀之控制組學生。
關鍵字：傳統啟蒙教材、故事繪本、中文識字能力、國語文學業成就




														英文摘要
													

Abstract
The primary purpose of this study was to explore whether the traditional enlightened teaching materials can promote the students’ Chinese verbal ability in the elementary schools. The second one was to explore the effects of the traditional teaching materials for promoting the literacy ability and the learning of Chinese and then some suggestions are provided according to the results of this study. 

Utilizing the quasi-experimental method, two classes of the first and third grade students of one elementary school are presented in this thesis. The students were divided into two groups of experimental group and control group and were taught with the traditional enlightened teaching materials and the reading instruction of picturebooks. The assessments in the research process are「Chinese Graded Word Reading Scale」and the Chinese examinations at school. Then the researcher compared the differences between these two groups of students’scores on the 「Chinese Graded Word Reading Scale」 and the examinations at school with one-way ANCOVA and analyzed the traditional enlightened teaching materials for promoting the first grade and third grade students’ learning effects of literacy ability and verbal ability. Meanwhile, the researcher interviewed the teachers and analyzed the learning feedback sheets from the students to understand the suggestions and what they have learned toward the traditional enlightened teaching materials. 

The research results show:
一、The Chinese literacy ability of the first grade students who learned traditional enlightened teaching materials is superior than the students who learned the reading of picturebooks. 
二、The Chinese literacy ability of the third grade students who learned traditional enlightened teaching materials is superior than the students who learned the reading of picturebooks. 
三、The learning effects of Chinese of the first grade students who learned traditional enlightened teaching materials is superior than the students who learned the reading of picturebooks.
四、The learning effects of Chinese of the third grade students who learned traditional enlightened teaching materials is superior than the students who learned the reading of picturebooks.

Keywords: traditional enlightened teaching material, picturebook, 
Chinese literacy, Chinese learning effect




